{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92d7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"233a"},"text":"§ 233a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual report on force structure changes exhibit for the defense budget","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92d8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Annual Report","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 10 days after the date on which the budget of the President for a fiscal year is submitted to Congress pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"section 1105 of title 31","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary of Defense shall submit to the congressional defense committees a report on any major weapon systems proposed to be divested, re-prioritized, or retired in such budget."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92d9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Contents","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Each report under subsection (a) shall include the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92da-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Identification of each major weapon system the Secretary of Defense proposes to divest, re-prioritize, or retire in the period of five fiscal years following the date of the report.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92db-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Budget line-item details related to each major weapon system identified under paragraph (1).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92dc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" For each proposed divestment, re-prioritization, or retirement, an explanation of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92dd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the timeline for the divestment, re-prioritization, or retirement, including any factors that may affect such timelines positively or negatively;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92de-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any cost savings associated with the divestment, re-prioritization, or retirement;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92df-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the rationale for the divestment, re-prioritization, or retirement, including a qualitative description of the risk associated with the divestment, re-prioritization, or retirement based on the most recent National Defense Strategy (as of the date of the report);","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92e0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any critical dependencies with other program efforts that might affect the timeline for such divestment, reprioritization, or retirement;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92e1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3/E"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"E"},"text":"(E)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the expected disposition of the weapon system after divestment, re-prioritization or retirement; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92e2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/b/3/F"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"F"},"text":"(F)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" identification of the system or systems that are expected to satisfy the military requirements that were fulfilled by the weapon system once the divestment, re-prioritization, or retirement of that weapon system is completed.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92e3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Relationship to Other Reports","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Defense shall ensure that the report required under subsection (a) is deconflicted with the report required under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s222e"},"text":"section 222e of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92e4-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s233a/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Major Weapon System Defined","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"In this section, the term “major weapon system” has the meaning given that term in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s101/a"},"text":"section 101(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida78d92e5-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/31/dA/tI/s151"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–31, div. A, title I, § 151","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2023-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 2023","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/137/179"},"text":"137 Stat. 179","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dA/tVIII/s811/c/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. A, title VIII, § 811(c)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/950"},"text":"139 Stat. 950","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida78d92e6-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida78d92e7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ida78d92e8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2025—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 101(a)” for “section 3455(f)”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
